WEBVTT

00:00:00.539 --> 00:00:03.358
I know this is going to sound strange,

00:00:03.382 --> 00:00:08.365
but I think robots can inspire us
to be better humans.

00:00:09.245 --> 00:00:12.339
See, I grew up in Bethlehem, Pennsylvania,

00:00:12.363 --> 00:00:14.301
the home of Bethlehem Steel.

00:00:14.991 --> 00:00:17.103
My father was an engineer,

00:00:17.127 --> 00:00:21.446
and when I was growing up,
he would teach me how things worked.

00:00:21.470 --> 00:00:23.564
We would build projects together,

00:00:23.588 --> 00:00:26.356
like model rockets and slot cars.

00:00:26.732 --> 00:00:29.640
Here's the go-kart that we built together.